<P>No, be you sure. For these are his wordes by the Psalmograph.<NOTE PLACE="marg">Psal. lxxxi<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"></NOTE> If they forsake my <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">aw, and walke not in my iudge|ments. If they breke my statutes, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">nd kepe not my co~manndeme~ts, I will visite their offences with
