<SP>
<SPEAKER>Philemon.</SPEAKER>
<P>In th<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> fourth boke of Moses, called N<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">mery, we reade that the pepole <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> Israel murmured and grudged <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">gainst God and against Mose<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">
