<P>I<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> this history many notable thin<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ges are to be learned. First, if a<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> such as God entendeth to saue, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word">
