<SP>
<SPEAKER>Ep.</SPEAKER>
<P>Why for me? Because good thinges haue chaunced vnto me? Because I haue passed ouer y^e daungerous sea, and am come vn+to the hauen of quietnes? Or be|cause I am deliuered from al euil and set in a blessed and ioyfull state? I thinke that at the buri|als
