<P>The maner among the Thracia~s is,<NOTE PLACE="marg">The maner of the Thra|cians.</NOTE> that whan any child is borne, and commeth into the world, thei wepe, lame~t &amp; mourn, but when it goeth out of y^e world, they reioyce and are mery.</P>
