<P>Then am I at a poynt w^t <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">he worldly possessions, &amp; I truste <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">n a good forewardnesse towarde God</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Chr.</SPEAKER>
<P>The custome in times <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ast was,<NOTE PLACE="marg">Monethes mindes and yeare minds</NOTE> y^t ther should be month <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">ndes &amp; yere minds kept for the <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ead.</P>
