<SP>
<SPEAKER>ph.</SPEAKER>
<P>Why so? Shall y^e know|ledge of Gods electe and chosen people be lesse in the kingdome of God, then it is in this world? We beinge in this corruptible bodye know one another, whan we see not God but with the eies of our faith,<NOTE PLACE="marg">ii. Cor. xii. i. Iohn. iii.</NOTE> &amp; shall we not know one an+other after that we haue put of
