</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Phi.</SPEAKER>
<P>That prayer is a necessary remedy for the auoyding of Sathans temp|tations, the holy scriptures teache manifestly in diuers places. Our sauior Christ saith,<NOTE PLACE="marg">Math. xxvi.</NOTE> watch &amp; pray, that ye fal not into temptation. A|gaine. This kind of deuils is not
<PB N="357" REF="186">
