1 word"> of him self: he hath saued me, be|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ause it was his pleasure to haue <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">e.<NOTE PLACE="marg">Psal. lvi.</NOTE> Againe he saith: Thou shalt
