</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Phi.</SPEAKER>
<P>Feare you not. God withoute all doubt hath sealed you by his holy spirite vnto euerlasting life. Your name is written in the boke of life. You are a citizin of the new glori|ous and heauenly Hierusalem. Yow shall remaine with God in glory after your departure for e|uer &amp; euer.<NOTE PLACE="marg">Of repenta~ce</NOTE></P>
</SP>
<SP>
