<P>The sentence whereunto they stick and cleue as vnto an inuincible bulwarke is this: A ma~ knoweth not whether he bee worthy loue or hatred, bu<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> althinges are kept vncerten vnto the time to come.</P>
