<P>When a man bele|ueth the gospel he is certaine of y^e remission of his sinnes, he is cer|ten of the fauour and good will o<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> God, and he is certaine also of e|uerlasting life. And he that lettet<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> go this faith, and falleth to doub<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ting,
