<P><NOTE PLACE="marg">Philip. 1.</NOTE>I moste hartely wyshe to bee losed from this life, and to be with Christ.<NOTE PLACE="marg">Iob. x.</NOTE> It greueth my soule lo~ger to liue in this mortall body.<NOTE PLACE="marg"><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ob. iii.</NOTE> And now, O Lord, dele with me accor+ding to thy will, and commaunde my spirit to be receiued in peace.
<PB N="513" REF="259">
For more expedient were it for me to die then to liue.</P>
