<P>In my body weaker and weaker, but I trust, in my soule stronger &amp; stron|ger. I pray you, lay me vp hier in my bed. For I begin to waxe very faint, and my wynde decreaseth &amp; waxeth shorter. I thanke you, it is wel. Neighbours I am troble|some vnto you, but I trust, I shal not be so long.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
